data.name: BibliographyDataField
desc: These values define parts of bibliographic data.
They are used to create a bibliography in a text document.
Depending on the type of the data some of the fields will usually be left empty.

items.name: IDENTIFIER
lines: This field contains a unique identifier for the bibliographic data.

items.name: BIBILIOGRAPHIC_TYPE
lines: This field contains the type of the bibliographic reference.
It is of the type BibliographyDataType.

items.name: ADDRESS
lines: This field contains the address of the publisher.

items.name: ANNOTE
lines: This field contains an annotation.

items.name: AUTHOR
lines: This field contains the name(s) of the author(s)

items.name: BOOKTITLE
lines: This field contains the title of the book.

items.name: CHAPTER
lines: This field contains the name or number of the chapter.

items.name: EDITION
lines: This field contains the number or name of the edition.

items.name: EDITOR
lines: This field contains the name(s) of the editor(s)

items.name: HOWPUBLISHED
lines: This field contains a description of the type of the publishing.

items.name: INSTITUTION
lines: This field contains the name of the institution where the publishing was created.

items.name: JOURNAL
lines: This field contains the name of the journal.

items.name: MONTH
lines: This field contains number or name of the month of the publishing.

items.name: NOTE
lines: This field contains a note.

items.name: NUMBER
lines: This field contains the number of the publishing.

items.name: ORGANIZATIONS
lines: This field contains the name of the organizations where the publishing was created.

items.name: PAGES
lines: This field contains the number(s) of the page(s) of the reference into a publishing.

items.name: PUBLISHER
lines: This field contains the name of the publisher.

items.name: SCHOOL
lines: This field contains the name of the university or school where the publishing was created.

items.name: SERIES
lines: This field contains the series of the publishing.

items.name: TITLE
lines: This field contains the title of the publishing.

items.name: REPORT_TYPE
lines: This field contains a description of the type of the report.

items.name: VOLUME
lines: This field contains the volume of the publishing.

items.name: YEAR
lines: This field contains the year when the publishing was created.

items.name: URL
lines: This field contains URL of the publishing.

items.name: CUSTOM1
lines: This field contains user defined data.

items.name: CUSTOM2
lines: This field contains user defined data.

items.name: CUSTOM3
lines: This field contains user defined data.

items.name: CUSTOM4
lines: This field contains user defined data.

items.name: CUSTOM5
lines: This field contains user defined data.

items.name: ISBN
lines: This field contains the ISBN data of the publishing.

items.name: LOCAL_URL
lines: This field contains a local copy of the publishing.
**since**
LibreOffice 7.3
